sequenceDiagram
    autonumber

    participant User as User / kubectl
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Webhook as Webhook Server<br/>9443/TCP HTTPS
    participant OMC as odh-model-controller<br/>Operator
    participant Route as OpenShift Route<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant NGC as NVIDIA NGC API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant NVCR as nvcr.io Registry<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Dashboard as RHOAI Dashboard
    participant MSA as model-serving-api<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS
    participant ModelReg as Model Registry<br/>HTTPS

    rect rgb(230, 240, 255)
        Note over User,Route: Flow 1: InferenceService Deployment
        User->>K8sAPI: POST InferenceService CR<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
        K8sAPI->>Webhook: Admission webhook call<br/>TLS (cert injection)
        Webhook-->>K8sAPI: Admit (validate name ≤53 chars)
        K8sAPI-->>User: InferenceService created
        OMC->>K8sAPI: Watch event received
        OMC->>K8sAPI: Create Route, Service,<br/>ServiceMonitor, KEDA TriggerAuth,<br/>ClusterRoleBinding<br/>Auth: SA Token
        K8sAPI-->>OMC: Resources created
        OMC->>ModelReg: Sync ISVC metadata<br/>Auth: Bearer Token, TLS 1.2+
        ModelReg-->>OMC: Metadata synced
        Note over Route: External clients access<br/>model via Route (TLS edge/reencrypt)
    end

    rect rgb(255, 243, 224)
        Note over User,NVCR: Flow 2: NIM Account Provisioning
        User->>K8sAPI: POST NIM Account CR<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
        K8sAPI->>Webhook: Validate singleton<br/>TLS (cert injection)
        Webhook-->>K8sAPI: Admit (one Account per ns)
        OMC->>K8sAPI: Watch event received
        OMC->>NGC: Validate NGC API key<br/>Auth: NGC API Key (Bearer)
        NGC-->>OMC: API key valid
        OMC->>NVCR: Get pull token<br/>Auth: NGC API Key (Basic)
        NVCR-->>OMC: Pull token
        OMC->>K8sAPI: Create Secret (ngc-secret),<br/>ConfigMap, Template<br/>Auth: SA Token
        K8sAPI-->>OMC: Resources created
    end

    rect rgb(232, 245, 233)
        Note over Dashboard,MSA: Flow 3: Gateway Discovery (Dashboard)
        Dashboard->>MSA: GET /api/v1/gateways<br/>Auth: Bearer Token, TLS 1.2+ (FIPS)
        MSA->>K8sAPI: SelfSubjectAccessReview<br/>(user's Bearer Token)
        K8sAPI-->>MSA: Access review result
        MSA->>K8sAPI: List Gateways<br/>Auth: SA Token
        K8sAPI-->>MSA: Gateway list
        MSA-->>Dashboard: Filtered gateways<br/>(per-user RBAC)
    end

    rect rgb(243, 229, 245)
        Note over OMC,K8sAPI: Flow 4: LLM Auth Policy Management
        Note over OMC: LLMInferenceService watch triggered
        OMC->>K8sAPI: Create AuthPolicy<br/>for HTTPRoute<br/>Auth: SA Token
        K8sAPI-->>OMC: AuthPolicy created
        OMC->>K8sAPI: Create EnvoyFilter<br/>for Gateway (Authorino TLS)<br/>Auth: SA Token
        K8sAPI-->>OMC: EnvoyFilter created
        Note over OMC: Kuadrant/Authorino enforce<br/>auth on live traffic via mTLS
    end
